description:
Zoro`s quick thinking - and a little help from a giant frog - sends the sea train soaring into the sky on a collision course with armed guards and their canine companions!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Find a Way Out! Rocketman Takes Flight!
Katsuro o Hirake! Sora o Tobu Rocketman!
Ouvrez le passage ! L`envol du Rocketman !
活路を開け! 空を飛ぶロケットマン!
